162
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:32,959
Should we all roll it and take the best one?

163
00:10:32,959 --> 00:10:33,599
Nope, one person.

164
00:10:33,599 --> 00:10:34,559
I will not roll.

165
00:10:38,079 --> 00:10:38,559
Sixteen.

166
00:10:42,079 --> 00:10:45,919
They tore us down mentally before breaking us physically.

167
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:49,919
We knew nothing except defeat was possible.

168
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:52,399
The wide portals.

169
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,959
